    "Likewise, we focused on studies published in the Software Engineering and Information Systems domains.",
    "However, we acknowledge that AI practitioners' perspectives on AI ethics might have been extensively studied in social sciences and humanities, areas we didn't explore -a limitation of our study.",
    "Future research can encompass studies from these domains.",
    "We decided to include only research-based articles in our grounded theory literature review (GTLR) study.",
